==English==

===Noun===
'''systematics'''

# {{systematics}} {{plurale tantum}} The [[science]] of [[systematic]] [[classification]], especially of [[organism]]s.  Depending on context this may be the same as [[taxonomy]] or distinct. In the latter case systematics will be taken to mean the research into the relationships of organisms, while taxonomy will involve itself in the recognition and the naming of taxa.

